about-description: I recently earned my AAS degree in Computer Information Systems, building on a passion for programming that started when I was 14. Over the years, I’ve developed a strong foundation in computer science principles and best practices, and I’m constantly exploring new languages, technologies, and ideas. I’m passionate about the endless possibilities for innovation and problem-solving that technology offers. I’m fluent in English and currently passionate in studying Japanese, which helps me connect with diverse audiences. My ultimate goal is to make a positive impact on the world through my work.
